.row
  .col-md-12.well
    %h3 Upload a new file:
    .input-group.text-center
      = form_tag({action: :create}, multipart: true) do
        = file_field_tag 'file'
        = submit_tag 'Upload', class: 'btn btn-primary btn-sm'

  .col-md-12
    %ul.list-group
      %li.list-group-item
        Upload limit 100MB.
        Supported extensions
        = [ImageFile, VideoFile].collect { |c| c.extensions }.flatten.join(', ')
        Videos will be truncated to 2.5mins
      %li.list-group-item
        Post via email to
        %string
          = current_user.magic_mail_address
        (multiple files up to 25MB in total). Subject and body being ignored.
      %li.list-group-item
        Download a vcard for your addressbook
        = link_to 'here', me_vcard_path
      %li.list-group-item
        Processing your image or video will take some time. You'll receive an email once it is ready to be published.
      %li.list-group-item
        Dropbox and box.net coming soon




